  "text": "The network has two recurrent loops: Elman recurrent loop where the hidden units from previous time step are copied to the input units; and Jordan recurrent loop where the network copies the output block [CITATION_1] . The architecture of the network is very similar to the one described in [CITATION_2] with the difference of the additional output and second recurrent loop.",
